<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">“Prayer for Graceful Words”</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Aug 09, 2017 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Holy God,
</p>

 <p>
In my haste to be heard, <br></br>
give me the strength <br></br>
to slow down, <br></br>
think carefully, <br></br>
and measure <br></br>
my words.
</p>

 <p>
Some words are poisonous fruit, <br></br>
and others are seeds of grace.
</p>

 <p>
Help me to sow <br></br>
according to your will.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


